  "title": "Outsource Associate",
  "description": "<p>Job Scope:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Book-keeping and preparation of management accounts</li>\n  <li>Preparation of Statutory report (Financial Statements and Notes to the accounts)</li>\n  <li>Preparation of custom reporting packages based on client requirements</li>\n  <li>Where clients are audited, provide support with respect to services provided to the client</li>\n  <li>Cash management and payment processing</li>\n  <li>GST preparation and filing</li>\n  <li>Payroll processing</li>\n</ul>\n<p>         - Preparation of payroll details (including calculation of OT, </p>\n<p>           allowances etc.)</p>\n<p>         - Payroll disbursement</p>\n<p>         - Leave management</p>\n<p>         - Preparation of IR8A and IR21</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Between 1 to 3 years of experience in accounting for Singapore entities of which at least 1 year of experience having handle full set of accounts</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of Singapore Financial Reporting Standards</li>\n  <li>Basic knowledge of Singapore payroll and taxation regulations</li>\n  <li>Knowledge and practical experience with various accounting systems</li>\n</ul>",
